    <item>
      <title>阿根廷前经济部长经营的对冲基金收益达 22%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/hedge-fund-run-by-former-argentina-economic-chief-posts-22-gain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2019 年，阿根廷总统毛里西奥·马克里的亲商政策即将终结，导致选举后混乱的抛售震动了该国资产，尼古拉斯·杜霍夫内辞去了阿根廷最高经济政策制定者的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/hedge-fund-run-by-former-argentina-economic-chief-posts-22-gain</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 13:58:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格塞斯拒绝让美国军队驻扎乌克兰并拒绝乌克兰未来加入北约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/hegseth-says-nato-membership-not-realistic-outcome-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部长皮特·赫格塞斯周三在对北约盟国的演讲中对美国对乌克兰的支持作出了严厉限制，拒绝了乌克兰加入北约的愿望，并拒绝了部署美国军队以帮助保证与俄罗斯的战争停火的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/hegseth-says-nato-membership-not-realistic-outcome-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 13:52:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔前往国会，特朗普呼吁降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-calls-for-lowering-interest-rates-as-powell-heads-to-hill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普呼吁降低利率，寻求对美联储施加更大压力，因为他正着手实施以关税和扩大减税为重点的第二任期经济议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-calls-for-lowering-interest-rates-as-powell-heads-to-hill</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 13:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰战争导致全球军备开支增至2.46万亿美元--IISS</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/world-defense-spending-soars-as-ukraine-war-continues-iiss-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际战略研究所在一份新报告中称，俄罗斯全面入侵乌克兰，导致全球军费开支到2024年将达到2.46万亿美元，增长7.4%，撒哈拉以南非洲是唯一的例外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/world-defense-spending-soars-as-ukraine-war-continues-iiss-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 11:03:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦肯锡表示，尽管特朗普颁布了 DEI 法令，公司仍将优先考虑多元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/mckinsey-strikes-defiant-tone-on-diversity-while-rivals-balk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令政府敦促私营企业放弃多元化、公平和包容性政策，但麦肯锡公司仍承诺将优先考虑员工队伍的多元化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/mckinsey-strikes-defiant-tone-on-diversity-while-rivals-balk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 09:10:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联邦机构解雇员工，称其为错误，再次解雇他们</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-sba-tells-staff-it-didn-t-mean-to-fire-them-then-fires-them-the-next-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的小企业管理局告诉试用期员工，它错误地向他们发送了解雇通知，并于第二天通知其中一些人，他们毕竟被解雇了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-sba-tells-staff-it-didn-t-mean-to-fire-them-then-fires-them-the-next-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 04:04:09 GMT</pubDate>
